messages.message: Hi Team, a prospect using AI Hub Build in demo environment is seeing ~20 sec response times per doc (10 fields on invoices) & wondered what our average responses times are in prod (Multi Tenant, in accordance with OpenAIs SLAs) ? @Lee this is Marc-Antoine from Pivot

CC <!subteam^S06395ZEFSL> to investigate. Can you share the prompts and a sample doc?
Also CC @Vishnu maybe that’s related to the reindexing issue you had looked into?
reindexing issue is in apps using refiner+ib_llm_tools. the Build app shouldn't have that issue after this fix (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C04TSMWLPAS/p1697226945724289) i believe.

Hi @Sławek Biel the prospect who fed that back to me is not the main user. Do you have any info I can share with him indepentenly of the prompts and doc (an invoice) as to why it takes that long and what it should be in prod?

We’d need more information to investigate if there is something wrong going on. How long are the documents, are these complex, or basic prompts? What release version is the demo environment?

I don’t know what the latency distribution on prod is. @Rakesh do we have a dashboard with that?
This a sample doc  (1 page) and the fields he’s looking to extract using basic prompts
I believe it's the latest release of the demo environment
@Nico can you share the docs with me ?
He only shared the above example with me. Do you need a full batch of sample docs?
Would be great to get some info on latency in prod if possible @Rakesh
